  "description": "<div id=\"product-detail\">\n\n    <h4>Application:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>2011-2017 Nissan Juke with 1.6L MR16DDT Turbocharged Engine</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h4>Features:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>High quality replacements for factory parts; excellent quality, durability, optimizing vehicle performance</li>\n        <li>OE design; simple replacement for factory part</li>\n        <li>Center rotating bearing housing designed to work with factory oil and coolant lines</li>\n        <li>Component dynamically balanced using state-of-the-art balancing machine (avg 0.5 mg or less)</li>\n        <li>Accessories included</li>\n        <li>1 year warranty for manufacturing defects</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Durable Compressor Wheel: 12(6+6) blades, Size: 38.3*51 mm</li>\n        <li>Turbine Wheel: 11 blades, Size: 37.7*43 mm</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h4>Turbo Part Numbers:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>49335-00850, 49335-00870, 49335-00893</li>\n        <li>49335-00880, 49335-00881, 49335-00882</li>\n        <li>49335-00883, 49335-00884, 49335-00885</li>\n        <li>49335-01800, 49335-01801, 49335-01810</li>\n        <li>49335-01811, 49335-00890, 49335-00891</li>\n        <li>49335-00892, 49335-00893, 49335-00894</li>\n        <li>TF035-00880, 4933500850, 1000050192</li>\n        <li>49135-09710, 4913509710, 49135-09700</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h4>O.E.M Numbers:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>14411-1KC0E, 144111KC0E, 14411-1KC1A, 144111KC1A</li>\n        <li>14411-1KC1B, 144111KC1B, 14411-1KC1C, 144111KC1C</li>\n        <li>14411-1KC1D, 144111KC1D, 14411-1KC1E, 144111KC1E</li>\n        <li>14411-1KC2A, 144111KC2A, 14411-1KC2B, 144111KC2B</li>\n        <li>14411-1KC2C, 144111KC2C, 14411-1KC2D, 144111KC2D</li>\n        <li>14411-1KC26, 144111KC26</li>\n    </ul>\n\n</div>\n",
